it.csi.mddtools.guigen
Interface TargetPlatform

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface TargetPlatform
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Target Platform'. specifica della target platform per cui deve essere generato il pacchetto, più altre caratteristiche tecniche.

The following features are supported:

  • Code
  • Enable Rich UI Behavior
  • Enable Fat Client
  • Portal Expositions
  • Wayf Profile
  • Security Profile

See Also:
GuigenPackage.getTargetPlatform()
